<table width=75%>
<tr><td bgcolor="#0000AF">
<strong><font color=white>
<center>Darkforge Greaves Quest</center>
</font></strong>
</td></tr>
</table><BR>
<div align="left">
1) Head to Cazic Thule and kill Lizarman Crusaders until you retrieve Right Decaying Greaves and Left Decaying Greaves.<BR>
<BR>
2) Head to Solusek A and retrieve 2 Melatite from the Sol Mining Co.<BR>
<BR>
3) Head to the Temple of Solusek Ro and give the items to the Undead Knight to receive the Darkforge Greaves.</div>
<BR>
