<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I started the darkforge quest around lvl 30.  This is the best lvl to start hunting in Cazic because of the need for invis. If you hunt in Cazic at below 30 and plan on going to a camp to collect some decayed p DON'T.  You will bring a train onto that group and will give sk's a bad name.  I have been questing for the items since lvl 30 and am currently 35 and still have 2 more decayed pieces to obtain.  The crusader spawn is RARE not random and they don't always drop the decayed.  Be warned if you come across a crusader they harm touch you always in first rounds of battle, so be sure to have a heal inc.</font></td></tr></table>
